snippet.title: Premortal VR - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Join our Discord https://discord.gg/uyas3EaNCW
Wishlist on Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/1903290?utm_source=youtube
Become a Patron https://www.patreon.com/premortalvr
Follow us on Twitter https://twitter.com/premortalvr

Premortal VR is an exploration and survival game set in a procedurally-generated world. Survive and explore the vast unique world. Gather valuable resources. Craft mighty weapons and armor. Sculpt the landscape as you see fit. Build villages and castles. Prepare well for your trials and ascend beyond!
